{
  "name": "TFYSwiftSegmentedKit",
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "summary": "一个功能强大且高度可定制的iOS分段控制框架，具有丰富的特性。",
  "description": "TFYSwiftSegmentedKit 2.0 — 纯 Swift、与 JXSegmentedView 解耦的\n分段控件 / 分页标签组件库。\n功能特点：\n* 12+ 指示器样式（Line/DoubleLine/Dot/Triangle/Rainbow/Background/\n  Gradient/GradientLine/Image/Capsule/ElasticLine/Blur/Symbol）\n* 标题渐变、图文混合、富文本、动态数字、角标、圆点\n* 拖拽重排、Context Menu、Long Press 钩子、触感反馈\n* 可访问性：自动订阅 Reduce Motion、accessibilityValue/hint、\n  WCAG 对比度校验\n* UICollectionViewDiffableDataSource 开关 / os_signpost 诊断\n* Combine Publishers + async selectItem(at:animated:)\n* SwiftUI：TFYSwiftSegmentedView 与 TFYSwiftPagingContainer\n* GitHub Actions CI（build / test-spm / lint / pod-lint）\n* Swift 5.9 / 6.0 · iOS 15+",
  "homepage": "https://github.com/13662049573/TFYSwiftSegmentedUilt",
  "license": {
    "type": "MIT",
    "file": "LICENSE"
  },
  "authors": {
    "田风有": "420144542@qq.com"
  },
